Spotify Desktop clone

This is a responsive Spotify desktop app clone built to replicate the core UI and UX of the original platform. It features a sleek, dark-themed interface with functional components such as a music library, playlists, artist views, and a playback control bar. The design includes interactive tabs, scrollable content, and dynamic rendering of music cards. Built with modern web technologies like Javascript, HTML and CSS.

To do list app

ThinkBoard is a sleek and intuitive to-do list app built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js). Designed for productivity, it allows users to effortlessly create, organize, and manage tasks with timestamps for better tracking. The clean, user-friendly interface ensures a seamless experience. Features like date-based sorting enhance efficiency, making it ideal for students, professionals, and anyone looking to streamline their daily routines.

Travell list

Far Away is a minimalist and efficient travel packing app designed to help users organize items for their trips with ease. The app allows seamless addition, removal, and tracking of packed items, complete with a progress tracker displaying the percentage of tasks completed. With a clean, user-friendly interface, it features sorting options and a clear list function for quick resets. Ideal for travelers, Far Away ensures nothing is forgotten by keeping a simple yet effective checklist.
